{"tid":1539912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例已經撤回 我收貨了","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:42:51.000Z","uid":237893,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"12b5ea706fb2f87c4cff0764b37cc311556b2406","tid":1539912,"uid":237893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"收你老母啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣就收貨 對唔對得住死左嘅義士<br />\n對唔對得住受傷嘅手足<br />\n對唔對得住呢三個月所有人流過嘅血汗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiE89kK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiE89kK.jpg&h=784155bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日收咗貨，明日就食屎，因為港共唔會再比機會你地有下一個自由之夏<br />\n心裡面有一絲閃過已經贏咗念頭嘅你，我要屌醒你!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f519bdf9611078fb81c1d2d49f9c13a608a8129c","tid":1539912,"uid":137157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"The FIVE demands of the protest<br />\n<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill <br />\n<br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality <br />\n<br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters <br />\n<br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\n    the Chief Executive <br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES."},{"pid":"59cad7673b481267ec581f27b41d253a2b624aae","tid":1539912,"uid":287387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"林鄭撤回目標係外國！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n外國少人知有五大訴求，以為香港人成功，林鄭目標係想阻人權法案通過！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加大國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢成功<img src=\"/as