,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"832e324282b13e1dae35123ea2909ad82e002655","tid":1539912,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700f6559b6a296f75ceb553a14954a83b42239e2","tid":1539912,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"九月八美國領事館有好多美國國旗？"},{"pid":"cc93dbe45d26734212dcf751ba920b0349c9ebc8","tid":1539912,"uid":20873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"而家睇形勢...星期六警犬係收斂<br />\n因為佢地怕左星期日個結果...<br />\n所以星期六大家要企出黎...證明香港仲係唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警權力太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7fd3b874adf8b71a17c4edff8755036d312d46","tid":1539912,"uid":49110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"求連仔改版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次入到連登，有好多大量重要訊息沉底，訊息太多，亂到睇唔到。依家打緊仗，重要訊息對任何人都很重要，是時候改版吧？訊息混亂對手足無好處。<br />\n如加&ldquo;克警戰術分析(知己知彼)&rdquo;、&ldquo;向高官致意(高官咁好，要做返D野回敬佢哋)&rdquo;、&ldquo;黨共小動作/陰謀背後&rdquo;、&ldquo;國際文宣/頭版團&rdquo;、&ldquo;發夢戰術&rdquo;、&quot;發夢裝備&quot;、&ldquo;夢後感想&rdquo;、&ldquo;夢後檢討&rdquo;、&ldquo;訓得唔好區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;、&ldquo;文宣空間&rdquo;、&ldquo;和你飛活動空間&rdquo;、&ldquo;和你衝總部&rdquo;、&ldquo;勇武有野話&rdquo;、&ldquo;狗嘅黑材料&rdquo;、&ldquo;戰場最前線！&rdquo;、&ldquo;對應藍絲/鄉黑暴落格&rdquo;、&ldquo;黑媒/紅媒清算車&rdquo;、&ldquo;戰區好人好事&rdquo;、&ldquo;識別鬼踪&rdquo;、&ldquo;被捕回憶錄&rdquo;、&ldquo;地鐵巴士遇難記&rdquo;(名就是但改)<br />\n<br />\n每分鐘，有一百幾十任何人放野上嚟(我係狗就放垃圾訊息，而且狗有一群十幾個都夠死)，咁真係唔係辦法！最要訊息分分鐘等下世先睇到！雖然好煩重，可否搵人做管理員必要時轉訊息到適當地方！<br />\n亂對我哋，對前線好不利！<br />\n我一時, 不吐不快,不喜勿插。<br />\n不妨考慮下，幫手推下....或改改內容然後推，推到連仔改版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}